    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Field photographs of the basidiomata of (a–c) Agaricus endoxanthus. (d–e) A. melanocarpus. (f) A. punjabensis. (g–h) A. xanthodermulus. Scale bars: a–c = 20 mm, d–e = 10 mm, f = 20 mm, g = 15 mm, h = 10 mm. Photographed by: E. Tarafder" ;
